(Non-blocker; we can try it out and revisit later:) This could end up creating many top-level _lsp_...<client> vars. That's pretty noisy. It might be worth the trouble to define a single _lsp_enable table and manage things in there, e.g.

```
_lsp_enable = {
  client = { [42] = true, [78] = true, ... },
